    "MissionTokens": {
        "Title": [
            "personnel change",
            "cleaning house",
            "early retirement",
            "one last trip",
            "rest in peace",
            "final destination"
        ],
        "Description": [
            "There was an 'accident' and now there's a couple of boxes of remains where they shouldn't be. [Client] need a cleaner to cart them off-world. [Timed]And don't tell me what you do with them. It's probably better if I don't know.",
            "The [Client] had a change of leadership and their former manager's been made redundant right through the eyes. Now they need someone to \"clear out the desk,\" so to speak, and dump everything off-world. [Timed]Really makes me appreciate being self-employed.",
            "Bit of a going away party / funeral that I want you to attend. The guest of honor needs a ride off-world and you're gonna give it to 'em. Dead bastard really should have known better than to skim from the [Client]. [Timed]",
            "Guess there was a bit of a disagreement between a couple of [Client] that got pretty heated. Anyway, they need someone to escort whatever's left of the losing side off the premises. [Timed]",
            "One of the big truths in this 'verse is that dead bodies seldom go anywhere on their own. That's why the [Client] need us to move one for them. I'm sure you can figure out somewhere suitably private to take the remains. [Timed]"
        ],
        "ObjectiveSetup": [
            "[Item]"
        ],
        "Timed": [
            "The longer this sits, the more likely someone who shouldn't stumbles across it. Can't risk that. Not to mention the stench.",
            "The [Client] are a little on edge about the remains just sitting out there. I've told them there's nothing to worry about, but let's go ahead and take care of this as fast as possible.",
            "We need to hurry up and take care of this before before someone starts poking around.",
            "Gonna call this a rush job. Remain are not going anywhere, but the [Client] will feel a lot better once everything's been taken care of.",
            "Don't take too long on this. Last thing we need is for someone else to get to the remains before you do."
        ],
        "Client": [
            "Nine Tails",
            "Dusters",
            "Low Riders",
            "NovaRiders"
        ]
    },
